---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="w-full py-16 px-8 mt-20 bg-slate-100 border-t border-slate-200/10">
	<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
		<div class="lg:col-span-2">
			<div class="text-lg italic text-slate-800 mb-6" style="font-family: var(--font-headline)">
				Room701
			</div>
			<p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
				Room701 — Engineering, Analytics &amp; Logic.
				複雑な世界を論理の力で紐解き、分析し、確かなシステムとして構築する。
			</p>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h5 class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-on-surface mb-6" style="font-family: var(--font-label)">Services</h5>
			<ul class="space-y-4 list-none p-0">
				<li><a class="text-slate-500 hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors underline decoration-amber-500/30 underline-offset-4 text-sm" href="/about">System Development</a></li>
				<li><a class="text-slate-500 hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors underline decoration-amber-500/30 underline-offset-4 text-sm" href="/about">Data Analytics</a></li>
				<li><a class="text-slate-500 hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors underline decoration-amber-500/30 underline-offset-4 text-sm" href="/about">Security &amp; Legal Governance</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h5 class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-on-surface mb-6" style="font-family: var(--font-label)">Blog</h5>
			<ul class="space-y-4 list-none p-0">
				<li><a class="text-slate-500 hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors underline decoration-amber-500/30 underline-offset-4 text-sm" href="/blog">Articles</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200/5">
		<p class="text-xs text-slate-500" style="font-family: var(--font-label)">
			&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Room 701. Engineering, Analytics &amp; Logic.
		</p>
	</div>
</footer>
<style>
	footer {
		padding: 2.5rem 1rem 4rem 1rem;
		background: var(--surface-container-low);
		color: var(--on-surface-variant);
		text-align: center;
	}
	.grid {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.35rem;
	}
	.brand {
		margin: 0;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--on-surface);
	}
	.desc,
	.copy {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.92rem;
	}
</style>
